description._content: Description: View from the Anse Etoile Road Location: Seychelles Date: 1890-1909 Description: General View of Victoria from "English River" Location: Seychelles Date: 1890-1909 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/770 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
